race.comment: ALL INCLUSIVE (1) resumes for the premier yard and has won 2/3 fresh. Expect him to be wound up and Todd's booking adds to the confidence. Maps to get every chance and he is a solid each-way proposition. FAST FREEZE (2) was seeking the hat-trick last start but didn't quite finish it off in a 64 over longer. She will be sharper today and expect her to get back on track. ACHACHA (7) deserved the win this grade over 1000m.  Finds a suitable race and should be in the finish again. MISS BLACK DIAMOND (5) placed behind the above first-up and is improved. Has placed 4/5 second up and fitter is in the mix.
